target_id: IRSwapExampleIndividuals.rdf version of this ontology was modified to use the Commons Ontology Library (Commons) rather than the OMG's Languages, Countries and Codes (LCC) and to eliminate redundancies in FIBO as appropriate.
This ontology provides examples of how to represent individuals for interest rate swaps and swap legs based on the Mizuho mocked-up sample data provided in the FIBO wiki.
IRSwapExampleIndividuals.rdf version of the ontology was modified to use the Commons Ontology Library (Commons) Annotation Vocabulary rather than the OMG's Specification Metadata vocabulary.
unique swap identifier for sample swap contract IY7VKEUR45886
contract IY7VKEUR45886 swap leg 1 that is a fixed interest rate leg
contract leg 2 IY7VKEUR45886 floating interest rate
contract leg 2 interest payment terms IY7VKEUR45886
IRSwapExampleIndividuals.rdf version of the ontology was modified to replace concepts from several FIBO FND ontologies with their counterparts added to the Commons Ontology Library (Commons) v1.1.

IRSwapExampleIndividuals.rdf version of this ontology was revised to replace uses of hasTag in Relations with hasTag from LCC, as the more complex union of datatypes in the Relations concept is not needed here.
